text: The Institution of Structural Engineers (IStructE) is an organisation for structural engineering based in the United Kingdom. It has 23,600 members in 105 countries.http://www.istructe.org/AboutIStructE/Pages/default.aspx The Institution is a learned body and provider of professional accreditation for structural engineers. The Institution publishes a monthly journal, The Structural Engineer. ==References== ==Other websites== *www.istructe.org – Official website *www.istructe.ie – Republic of Ireland Branch website *Structural Awards 07 Category:Organisations based in London
